# Privacy Policy for "Kirana Nondi"

Effective Date: 04 Oct, 2025
Application Name: Kirana Nondi

## Introduction

Kirana Nondi is an Android application designed to help users manage their daily grocery and kirana-related records with ease. We value your trust and are fully committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines our practices and clearly explains that the Kirana Nondi app does not collect, use, or store any personal information from its users.

## Data Collection

Kirana Nondi does not collect, request, or store any kind of personal information from its users.

No user data is collected by the app.

## Data Usage

Since we do not collect any user data, no data is used for any purpose. Specifically:

* No analytics are performed.
* No data is used for advertising.
* No data is shared with third parties.

Your use of the app is completely private and independent.

## User Rights

Because no data is collected, you maintain full privacy and complete control over your personal information. The Kirana Nondi app has no access to your personal data at any point.

## Security Measures

Although Kirana Nondi does not collect data, we ensure that the app is built with secure coding practices to safeguard user experience and prevent unauthorized access or misuse of the application.

## Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy in the future if the functionality of the app changes. Any modifications will be clearly communicated by updating this page within the app or through other appropriate channels. We encourage users to review this Privacy Policy periodically to stay informed.

## Contact Us

